<section class="w-full py-12 md:py-20 px-4 sm:px-6 bg-white">
    <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto relative overflow-hidden rounded-3xl bg-linear-to-br from-[#001F5B] via-[#001F5B] to-[#00BCD4] shadow-2xl">

        <div class="absolute top-0 right-0 -translate-y-1/2 translate-x-1/2 w-64 h-64 md:w-96 md:h-96 bg-white/5 rounded-full blur-3xl"></div>
        <div class="absolute bottom-0 left-0 translate-y-1/2 -translate-x-1/2 w-48 h-48 md:w-64 md:h-64 bg-[#00BCD4]/10 md:bg-[#00BCD4]/20 rounded-full blur-2xl"></div>

        <div class="relative z-10 p-10 md:p-16 text-center lg:text-left flex flex-col lg:flex-row items-center justify-between gap-8 lg:gap-10">

            <div class="max-w-2xl space-y-4 md:space-y-6">
                <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl lg:text-5xl font-extrabold text-white tracking-tight leading-tight">
                    ¿Listo para fortalecer la <span class="text-[#00BCD4]">gestión pública</span> de tu entidad?
                </h2>
                <p class="text-base md:text-lg lg:text-xl text-slate-200 font-medium leading-relaxed">
                    Únete a los más de 5,000 profesionales que ya transformaron su desempeño con Inhouse Perú. Asegura el cumplimiento de las directivas de control interno hoy mismo.
                </p>
            </div>

            <div class="w-full lg:w-auto flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-4 shrink-0 justify-center">
                <a
                        href="https://wa.link/vpjt0m"
                        target="_blank"
                        rel="noopener noreferrer"
                        class="w-full lg:w-auto px-10 py-5 bg-[#00BCD4] text-white font-bold rounded-xl shadow-lg shadow-[#00BCD4]/30 hover:bg-white hover:text-[#001F5B] hover:scale-105 transition-all duration-300 text-center text-lg"
                >
                    Empezar ahora
                </a>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>